CONNERS MARINE CO., Inc., as Owner of THE Barges MARTHA HARRINGTON and MAY W, Libelant-Appellant, v. THE Steam Tug NAT SUTTON, Hedger Transportation Co., Inc., Claimant-Appellee. No. 96. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 5, 1932. Oourtland Palmer, of New York City, for appellant. Single & Hill, of New York City (Thomas H. Middleton, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
